content.name: QUEENZ: The Show with BALLS!

primaryPhoto.description:
The trailblazing, life affirming, live vocal, drag extravaganza QUEENZ: THE SHOW WITH BALLS is taking the UK by storm and coming to the Dominion Theatre for one night only!
Direct from their smash-hit sell-out UK tour, this sequin-clad pop party serves up ‘mind-blowing’ LIVE vocals and a set list of Britney, Whitney and everything in between.
These dragtastic divas will have you feeling fierce and fabulous before you know it as they close their Spring 2024 tour with one final massive party BACK in London’s West End.
Book your QUEENZ: THE SHOW WITH BALLS theatre tickets with LOVEtheatre today!
